{"tid":1866221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"就嚟到超級大三罷，返工撚應當悔改","createTime":"2020-02-06T15:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T05:10:18.000Z","uid":320676,"like":125,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"4d17d7f1080df6f29ffa05f4946309cf8cc568cb","tid":1866221,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:30:59.000Z","msg":"記唔記得之地鐵工會，城巴新巴工會已經講咗要求政府回應醫護罷工，如果無合理答覆就會大罷工，行動升級<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺連登 FB IG自稱黃絲，自稱支持醫護嘅返工撚，立即悔改，立即罷工。<br />\n<br />\n你如果再返工，只係傳播肺炎，白費罷工手足一番心機，佢哋想封關保護你，你就白費佢哋心機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你班黃絲返工撚知唔知道你哋喺85開始害死咗幾多人？有幾多件浮屍係你哋間接產生？而家已經係最後嘅悔改機會，立即罷工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你再返工就只會中肺炎死</span></span>"},{"pid":"c76a5ab1814f81d6ac398c9321b716c59b3aee10","tid":1866221,"uid":320676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:32:26.000Z","msg":"無晒地鐵巴士都仲返到工嘅人都幾勁"},{"pid":"9954a6845fb1f84d3c78182be5bdecb644f0979a","tid":1866221,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c76a5ab1814f81d6ac398c9321b716c59b3aee10","tid":1866221,"uid":320676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:32:26.000Z","msg":"無晒地鐵巴士都仲返到工嘅人都幾勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:33:05.000Z","msg":"不過咁勁就會快啲中肺炎死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2a29faea616d578d7c8f893ac4ca2b22d0bc28","tid":1866221,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"年初一到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4619f99c0631b54be547b750671fa0d85424f26","tid":1866221,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:34:19.000Z","msg":"見到有人無口罩都去黨鐵站真係唔怕死"},{"pid":"df0591eaf36ddec6931aa1878553207f2f3438b2","tid":1866221,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c76a5ab1814f81d6ac398c9321b716c59b3aee10","tid":1866221,"uid":320676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:32:26.000Z","msg":"無晒地鐵巴士都仲返到工嘅人都幾勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"行路唔得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd16afc9b6bf92468eb5c0f38362de39e057ab06","tid":1866221,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d2a29faea616d578d7c8f893ac4ca2b22d0bc28","tid":1866221,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"年初一到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:35:13.000Z","msg":"做得好，你中肺炎機會低好多"},{"pid":"f4dd57ee022f0ab88678e6b9a2aab5f2424fa64d","tid":1866221,"uid":320676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:38:02.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】政府昨日宣布，由今日凌晨起暫停在羅湖、落馬洲支線、落馬洲皇崗和港澳客輪碼頭4個口岸服務。唯旅客仍可經機場、深圳灣、港珠澳大橋及啟德郵輪碼頭出入境。巴士業職工會聯盟批評政府仍拒絕全面封關，措施直接增加對巴士前線人員的威脅，正醞釀發動罷工或工業行動。<br />\n<br />\n巴士業職工會聯盟在社交網帖文，批評政府拒絕全面封關，只將人流集中經深圳灣口岸及港珠澳大橋口岸入境，直接增加對巴士前線人員的威脅。認為香港政府必須果斷執行全面封關，限制任何國籍的旅客經中國疫區入境來港，堵截隱性患者將武漢肺炎病毒輸入境內，從而確保醫療資源能應付本港的抗疫工作。<br />\n<br />\n巴士業職工會聯盟指，假如醫護界罷工未能打動政府「拒絕全面封關」之決定，就保障業界從業員健康及公眾利益著想；將開展籌備緊急會員大會表決通過罷工或工業行動。"},{"pid":"a39366bc305cd9fd9a7518dae489e70724f68824","tid":1866221,"uid":320676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"港鐵新動力：<br />\n<br />\n各位鐵路人，大家堅持左40年，盡心盡力帶畀乘客安全安心嘅乘車體驗，如今公司回覆工會聯署信話要「配合政府」，寧願全港市民攬炒都唔表態！仲忍！<br />\n<br />\n重申強烈要求管方促政府全面封關以保障公司同事健康及人身安全！各位會員/非會員同事，如今確診個案已新增至12宗，6宗由高鐵傳入，1宗返港時有乘坐過東鐵綫及馬鞍山綫。懷疑個案更超過670宗，有專家已表明社區或已出現隱形患者，源頭堵截乃當下燃眉之急。齊心則事成，今日醫管局主席向政府作出呼籲「進一步減少中港兩地人流」，並非無故之舉動，乃一眾醫管局員工陣線工會會員上下齊心凝聚力量之初果；同事，疫情並非「等一下」就會消失或得到處理，疫情需要嚴謹控制再加源頭預防才能看到輕微曙光⋯工會要人，一定要齊心，才有足夠施壓的效果，工會要人！<br />\n<br />\n港鐵新動力現時正式向會員召開《特別會員大會》，以一同商議及表決工會將會舉行的工業行動，其中包括工業行動的形式及實際操作內容。<br />\n<br />\n未成為會員的同事，請把握時間凝聚力量，加入工會！多你一個非常重要！請立即網上填妥表格加入我們！未來一個星期理事們會盡力舉辦不同位置既快閃入會，請繼續留意本會最新資訊！<br />\n<br />\n《特別會員大會》需於發起後30日內召開，經考慮到輪班工作及辦公室時間上班的會員，及事情的急切性，理事會謹訂如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：2020年2月7日(星期五)<br />\n時間：17:30-19:00<br />\n地點：旺角道7-9 號威特商業大廈9 樓 學聯<br />\n（或於理事會認為合適的地方）<br />\n<br />\n請會員盡快填寫以下問卷以便理事會統計將會出席《特別會員大會》的人數，及初步了解各會員對工業行動之意向。<br />\n<br />\n✍🏻港鐵新動力-會員工業行動可接受程度問卷<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/J1x7ivUr4KCr2yQg9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJ1x7ivUr4KCr2yQg9&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=77bd2848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/J1x7ivUr4KCr2yQg9</a>"},{"pid":"6f050467253647e359d7931a311c23b1684ed2a6","tid":1866221,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:39:58.000Z","msg":"香港人，罷工！"},{"pid":"84715e5b006b07f923ceecd3f97b60c95385eb2a","tid":1866221,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:41:24.000Z","msg":"我今日就見到好多人返工放工，其實我好驚，呢班人真係會將病毒帶到我條邨，到時社會爆發呢班人就有好多責任"},{"pid":"abcb1b676a679d6673b65642093dbee34d54ae06","tid":1866221,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"你每返一次工就可能消耗2-3個口罩<br />\n而你罷工就唔洗消耗口罩，慳好多口罩"},{"pid":"7552f36239d5fb046a417f2997436e71b1c1447a","tid":1866221,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:44:21.000Z","msg":"求下你哋罷工啊，我求你哋呀"},{"pid":"3a7584f2ce2b594ce947ba926d6d5713883e49c5","tid":1866221,"uid":102491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"fe3f914ec5fce16f0faedb9e26e59c583d403c22","tid":1866221,"uid":320676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3a7584f2ce2b594ce947ba926d6d5713883e49c5","tid":1866221,"uid":102491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:48:10.000Z","msg":"推！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:50:32.000Z","msg":"無人推<br />\n<br />\n三罷當日頭條：「全港交通癱瘓，大量市民步行到公司上班」"},{"pid":"18feb5e627400df182900407526f68960e34532d","tid":1866221,"uid":320676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:52:25.000Z","msg":"封關封關封關 罷工罷工罷工"},{"pid":"e163ffc0578c593cfa5419eb3c21d5d1f9e4a029","tid":1866221,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T17:56:19.000Z","msg":"大家幫手行多步宣傳下比你ig,fb,tg,Twitter 同身邊既朋友。<br />\n<br />\n加入工會，組織力量<br />\n⚠️工會大全⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=5cdac5f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n要求唔比🐶用電槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-konger-strongly-hope-usa-can-warning-hong-kong-police-cant-adding-electric-gun-new-weapon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-konger-strongly-hope-usa-can-warning-hong-kong-police-cant-adding-electric-gun-new-weapon&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=85e4741e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-konger-strongly-hope-usa-can-warning-hong-kong-police-cant-adding-electric-gun-new-weapon</a><br />\n<br />\n阻止政府強行通過國歌法<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-governments-hard-pressed-national-anthem-law-violates-one-country-two-systems-and-freedom-speech\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-governments-hard-pressed-national-anthem-law-violates-one-country-two-systems-and-freedom-speech&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=10d24628\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-governments-hard-pressed-national-anthem-law-violates-one-country-two-systems-and-freedom-speech</a><br />\n<br />\n聯署要求世衛主席辭職<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/